title: Microsoft Office 2010 - No Key Needed
description:
Developer: Microsoft
Initial release: June 15, 2010 (2010-06-15)
Stable release Build: 14.0.4763.1000 / June 15, 2010; 3 months ago (2010-06-15)
Operating system: Windows 7, Windows Server 2008, Windows Vista with Service Pack 1, Windows Server 2003 R2, Windows XP with Service Pack 3 (32-Bit only)
Platform: Microsoft Windows (Intel x86 32-bit/64-bit)

Double click the setup.exe file and follow the wizard. No CD key, crack or patch required for initial installation
